{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Hybrid: Command Center + Smart Sections\n      Best of both — hero KPIs up top, sectioned content below\n      3 hero KPI cards with sparklines at the top (Omzet, Winst, Belasting). Below: two clear sections — \"Overzicht\" with the revenue chart + cost donut side by side, and \"Aandachtspunten\" with contextual alerts (ongefactureerd, openstaand, uren, documenten) that only appear when relevant. Secondary metrics (Km, Uren, Documenten) become a compact icon-strip, not full cards. Quick actions integrated into the header area.\n      \n        Pros\n          Hero KPIs give instant pulse check\n          Sections create logical grouping without forcing a narrative\n          Contextual alerts = zero noise when things are fine\n          Compact secondary strip avoids card bloat\n          Still fits on one screen without excessive scrolling\n        \n        Cons\n          Slightly more complex layout logic","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1774016422719}
